long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Change default search engine to make AllFindSeek your search in Chrome browser address bar (omnibox).

To get a new search experience, you only need to install this extension and leave it as the default search in the address bar.

Features of the extension:
- Free and safe Google Chrome extension
- Ðžne-click installation, small size and minimum browser resource usage
